snippet.title: Enemy of the Surveillance State
snippet.description: Privacy is a God-given right. Mass surveillance — whether done by an overreaching  government agency or a nosy corporation — is an infringement of that right. The Enemy of the [Surveillance] State podcast is a weekly episodic program geared toward sharing news, tools, and practices to help you protect your personal data against mass surveillance.
